    "text": "Postal Executive Accountability Act - Prohibits bonuses or other rewards to the Postmaster General or any other officer of the U.S. Postal Service (USPS) in a senior executive position in any year in which any postal retail facility or mail processing facility is closed.\n\nRepeals exceptions to the limit on total compensation for USPS officers and employees."
